message.content:
1. The CAL package was evaluated for its effectiveness.
2. The evaluation was conducted on 32 childcare students.
3. The students involved in the evaluation were in the UK.
4. The students were randomised into two groups.
5. One group was assigned to watch the CAL package.
6. The other group was assigned to read an information leaflet.
7. The information leaflet contained the same information as the CAL package.
8. Each group consisted of 16 students.
